# VITE ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES — Firebase Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# STEP 1: Go to https://console.firebase.google.com
# STEP 2: Click "Add project" → name it "mind-over-matter" → Continue
# STEP 3: Click the web </> icon → Register app → copy the firebaseConfig
# STEP 4: In console: Build → Authentication → Get started → Email/Password → Enable
# STEP 5: Build → Firestore Database → Create database → Start in test mode
# STEP 6: Copy each value below from your firebaseConfig object
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=paste-your-apiKey-here
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=paste-your-authDomain-here
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=paste-your-projectId-here
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=paste-your-storageBucket-here
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=paste-your-messagingSenderId-here
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=paste-your-appId-here
